    dc:description "Figs 7–11. Spiniglans beveridgei sp. nov. 7. Scolex. 8. Hooks. 9. Mature proglottis. 10. Terminal genitalia. 11. Pregravid proglottis with young reticular uterus. Scale bars: 7 = 100 µm; 8 = 20 µm; 9 = 200 µm; 10 = 50 µm; 11 = 500 µm." ;
